{"tid":2250581,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消費800元換本地遊名額　旅發局「賞你遊」本地團料下月起陸續出發","createTime":"2020-10-20T08:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T09:07:03.000Z","uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef0622866a350ce4f2b40a8c172fa74821a45d7","tid":2250581,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"旅遊發展局因應政府放寬本地遊措施，推出「賞你遊香港」活動，市民今日起，在本地零售及餐廳商戶的實體店，以最多兩張收據計算，消費滿800元，可以換取一個本地遊的名額。 <br />\n<br />\n市民要自行儲起店舖發出的機印收據正本，下周二起憑收據向旅行社報名，並繳付每人100元按金，先到先得，按金可以在出發日取回。 <br />\n<br />\n旅遊局預計，「賞你遊」本地旅行團會陸續在下月起至年底出發，計劃提供約50個由不同本地旅行社設計的深度遊行程，全部都是半天或以上，會到訪最少兩個景點。 <br />\n<br />\n旅發局又指，參與的旅行社要向旅議會登記行程，並簽署《本地遊防疫承諾》，而旅行團智包括導遊服務、來回交通、一餐膳食，以及基本保險。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2362435&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEXwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=cdd5c2ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362435</a>"},{"pid":"68ac0688ce96cb050c279f3ec7c4f3a36d45d6bc","tid":2250581,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:02:09.000Z","msg":"藍店回血劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5329a077b2a630d94fd328e6d252276b22dcdbf7","tid":2250581,"uid":137493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12d5f53ff4ef473161616b81b93ddaa7e5394a95","tid":2250581,"uid":8461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5329a077b2a630d94fd328e6d252276b22dcdbf7","tid":2250581,"uid":137493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"利益輸送咋<br />\n益市民咩？你會唔會諗太多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},